{"tid":1393822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<發大財>  中國停簽赴台自由行      韓國瑜「很錯愕」 開罵民進黨挑撥兩岸","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:58:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db2e83c1d66829143842f9e05d7da7fd67e7b726","tid":1393822,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"中國停簽赴台自由行 韓國瑜「很錯愕」 開罵民進黨挑撥兩岸<br />\n<br />\n中國暫停47個城市來台自由行，韓國瑜開罵民進黨，指挑撥兩岸關係，人民要選擇發財道路。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜上午於高雄市社教館頒發95名校長聘書，會後先被問及郭台銘返國一事；韓國瑜說，嘗試與郭台銘董事長聯絡，目前還沒聯絡上，期待盡快拜訪。至於柯文哲組黨，韓國瑜說，尊重與祝福，台灣民主政黨眾多，預期台灣民眾黨政治力量（比一般政黨）大，柯P「肩膀上責任更重大」，期待告訴台灣人民追求理想跟方向。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，韓國瑜被問及陸客自由行，話鋒轉趨猛烈。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜一聽到媒體詢問對自由行中斷的看法時，直說感到「很錯愕」，不過接著大罵民進黨，指這3年執政一塌糊塗，貪污、腐敗、低效率並挑撥兩岸關係，不等於兩千三百萬台灣人，再次呼籲陸方持續開放兩岸交流。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，對於廣大台灣人民來說，兩岸互利雙贏是最好選擇，要選擇一條寬的路，不要選窄的，選一條經濟都能獲得幫助的發財道路，沒必要選擇貧窮、經濟不好道路，選擇快樂的路，不要選擇痛苦的路。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2870507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2870507&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=e013efc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2870507&h=d173ef8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2870507</a><br />\n<br />\n停發外遊簽證係中國<br />\n但依KMT 邏輯<br />\n千錯萬錯 都唔係中國錯"},{"pid":"9e33c1afcedbde29b507a690165fcab14f0a4f97","tid":1393822,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"支那瑜不出奇"},{"pid":"0fddbdf306666ab2851525f077c24795f8f54ab7","tid":1393822,"uid":148511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:15:32.000Z","msg":"唔該制裁埋我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2b914fb634ce344feb100e339b5489332852fb","tid":1393822,"uid":288297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"支那瑜不斷講及發大財，佢知唔撚知大陸仲有好撚多地方好撚窮啊"},{"pid":"f02dd9499254305b3caa388155059faf8a44a676","tid":1393822,"uid":35821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"台灣發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時制裁香港呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4988613724ddb8854a7130f3613d0e10e32afd05","tid":1393822,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"係時候去台灣喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963493ec30ae12b440123c7960b443e73afe85a7","tid":1393822,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}